### SRE Governance API - REST Client Tests
### Service URL
@baseUrl = https://sre-governance-api-557303580741.us-central1.run.app

### ============================================
### 1. Root Endpoint - API Documentation
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================
### 2. Health Check
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================
### 3. Get Users - Normal Response
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================
### 4. Chaos Test - Latency (3 second delay)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users?chaos=latency
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================
### 5. Chaos Test - Error (500 Internal Server Error)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users?chaos=error
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================
### Testing Notes:
### ============================================
# Click "Send Request" above any request to test
# 
# Expected Responses:
# - Root: API documentation with endpoints list
# - Health: {"status": "healthy", ...}
# - Users: {"users": [...], "count": 3, ...}
# - Chaos Latency: 3 second delay, then normal response
# - Chaos Error: {"error": "Internal Server Error", ...}
#
# For monitoring/alerts testing:
# - Run chaos=latency multiple times to trigger alert policy
# - Check Cloud Monitoring for latency spike
# - Check Cloud Logging for alert handler logs
